Big burly muscled smoothed tanned skin with bleached blonde hair.
If you think this is Zucan, you have to be crazy!
This guy is a childish wimpy looking guy with black hair and freckles.
He looks like he could hardly carry a feather. 
Often, as it may seem, he wounds himself with the wielded weapon.
But, the one thing he has got going for him is ....
     he is the luckiest son-of-a-bitch around!

